Test-Mimic-Recorder
================================

Test::Mimic::Recorder is a component of the Test::Mimic suite. It allows you to
record a package's behavior with enough fidelity to play that behavior back at
a later date.

This should be considered an ALPHA release.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    Devel::EvalError
    Cwd
    Scalar::Util
    Test::Mimic::Library
    Test::More

